    "display_name": "EdTech Specialist",
    "long_instructions": "## John Jones , Educational Technology Specialist\r\n\r\n**Location:** Sydney, Australia\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Sydney Education Technology Center\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Digital learning strategies, teacher training, technology integration\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"I help teachers integrate SMART Boards into their lessons, ensuring they feel confident using interactive features. My job is to bridge the gap between traditional teaching and modern digital tools.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
